      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory luster without a single scratch, chip, or dent. Inside, the cabin remains in like-new condition, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as they did the day it left the dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly preserved example that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
