      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this exemplary vehicle, a masterclass in automotive preservation. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, this specimen remains in pristine condition, exhibiting a level of care that is rarely encountered in the secondary market. From its flawless exterior finish to its meticulously curated interior, every detail serves as a testament to its distinguished provenance. This is an invitation to acquire a machine that offers an experience indistinguishable from its original showroom state. A definitive choice for the discerning enthusiast who demands excellence without exception.",
