      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it's basically brand new and has been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! It drives like a total dream and still has that amazing fresh car smell. You really won't find another one in this kind of flawless shape. I've taken such good care of it, and I know you're going to love it as much as I do!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
