    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade example that truly defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing no signs of wear or age. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory shine, completely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and the interior still carries a hint of that new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the adaptive driver aids, functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented, full-service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. This is a turn-key opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
